Class TurtleWorld

java.lang.Object
  exploris.gui.Viewer
      exploris.aquarium.TurtleWorld
          TurtleWorld

public class TurtleWorld
extends TurtleWorld

A TurtleWorld represents a world within which Turtles can move around. Unlike the class declaration that describes Turtles, the one that describes TurtleWorlds does instruct the computer on how they can be visually represented.
